rows.label: tev001511_MSG0010
rows.name:
The whole universe might be going
down the crapper, but that doesn't
change anything for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001511_MSG0020
rows.name:
What's that saying? "Money is the best
lawyer in hell?" ...So anyway, you wanted
something from me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001511_MSG0050
rows.name:
I don't know what that says about you,
but it's all good by me. Let's get to it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001511_MSG0080
rows.name:
Whenever something big goes down, you
can be sure there's money in it. You ever
catch a whiff of that, you come to me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001511_MSG0100
rows.name:
I've been waiting for you here for so long,
I thought I was beginning to going gray.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001511_MSG0110
rows.name:
But don't worryâ€”I'll bill you for those
hours later. Be sure to pay up promptly.
You wouldn't like the interest rate...[ST:wait ]
